# PR Checklist (must be satisfied before merge)

## Scope
- Change is limited to requested task.
- No unrelated refactors.

## Quality gates
- Lint passes (if configured).
- Tests pass (existing + new/updated relevant tests).
- Build/typecheck passes (if configured).

## Risk control
- Backward compatibility considered.
- No secrets introduced.
- Config/infra/auth/db migration changes explicitly approved.

## PR description must include
1. Summary of changes
2. Motivation
3. Verification steps + results
4. Risks and rollback notes
5. Follow-up tasks (if any)
